This paper is about robot navigation, which is a subfield of robotics (cs.RO). The method proposed in the paper involves reinforcement learning (cs.AI) and probabilistic roadmaps (cs.SY), which are both common techniques in robotics. The paper also evaluates the method in simulation, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV) techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO, followed by cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY, and cs.CV.
